sources.description:
Invasion from Outer Space!...Sights too weird to imagine! Destruction too monstrous to escape!
An uptight, leather-clad female alien, armed with a ray gun and accompanied by a menacing robot, comes to Earth to collect Earth's men as breeding stock.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/TA83HKMFpow
Title: Devil Girl from Mars (1954)

Director: David MacDonald
Writers: John C. Mather, James Eastwood
Stars: Hugh McDermott, Hazel Court, Peter Reynolds & Patricia Laffan
Genres: Horror, Sci-Fi, Psychotronic

00:00 - Full movie with subtitles
05:20 - A Martian spacecraft crash-lands near a Scottish inn during a storm, trapping guests inside.
15:45 - Commander Nyah reveals her mission to abduct Earth men for Martian repopulation.
25:30 - Nyah's robot Chani disintegrates a fleeing guest to demonstrate Martian power.
35:15 - Michael Carter and Ellen Prestwick attempt escape but hit Chani's force field barrier.
50:10 - Professor Hennessey discovers Nyah's vulnerability to Earth's atmosphere.
1:00:05 - Albert Jamieson sacrifices himself to damage Chani with a fire axe.
1:10:40 - Michael exploits Chani's damaged circuits to breach Nyah's suit, triggering self-destruct.
